{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"clearNotificationCenter"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)clearNotificationCenter","roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"clearNotificationCenter","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"clearNotificationCenter","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"clearNotificationCenter","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes all notifications delivered by your app from the iOS Notification Center."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This is commonly used when:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"User opens the app (clear notifications since they’re viewing content)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"User logs out (clear notifications for privacy)","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Content is marked as read in-app","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Performing a “mark all as read” action"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Only removes notifications from your app; other apps’ notifications are unaffected."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Clear notifications on app activation and logout:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationManager {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive() {","        \/\/ Clear notifications when user opens app","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Also reset badge","        UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = 0","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(0)","    }","","    func handleUserLogout() {","        \/\/ Clear notifications for privacy","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Unregister from push","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { _ in }","","        \/\/ Clear user identity","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(\"\")","    }","","    func markAllAsRead() {","        \/\/ Clear from notification center","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Update backend","        APIClient.shared.markAllNotificationsRead { _ in }","","        \/\/ Clear badge","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(0)","    }","}"]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/clearnotificationcenter"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/clearNotificationCenter"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Clears all delivered notifications from the notification center."}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/document